title: In 'unprecedented' action, Putin orders nuclear deterrent forces to be on 'high alert' amid spiraling tensions over Ukraine - NBC News
content: In 'unprecedented' action, Putin orders nuclear deterrent forces to be on 'high alert' amid spiraling tensions over Ukraine  NBC NewsView Full Coverage on Google News
description: The Russian premier said in a meeting of top officials that the move was in response to leading NATO powers making what he called “aggressive statements.”
